data.Name: Sin Eater
data.Bio: Sin Eater is a progressive Hardcore band from San Antonio, Texas. They are signed to Wartime Records and have released 2 EPs, their latest being "A Place Between Life and Living". You can download their music here. http://www.sineater.bandcamp.com Vox - Matty Guitar - Jose Guitar - Joshua Drums - Dom Bass - Adrian Read more on Last.fm
